Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/deaygo/dotfiles.git

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/dotfiles/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/.vim ~/.vim
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/.i3 ~/.i3
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/.bash_aliases ~/.bash_aliases
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/.bashrc ~/.bashrc
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/bin ~/bin
